    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor signs of regular use, such as small stone chips, while the interior remains comfortable and tidy. Mechanically, it is solid and performs reliably, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a dependable car that is ready for the road. You can expect a well-maintained vehicle that balances quality and value perfectly.",
