    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a reliable and comfortable choice for a daily driver. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. While the exterior and interior are generally clean, you may find minor cosmetic blemishes such as small paint chips or light interior wear consistent with regular use. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road.",
